# Superpowers (global)

This workspace uses [obra/superpowers](https://github.com/obra/superpowers) v5.1.0 globally (`~/.cursor/skills/`).

## Before implementation

- New feature or ambiguous request → invoke **brainstorming** (or project `/design-system` for GDD systems).
- Approved design → **writing-plans**; execution → **subagent-driven-development** or **executing-plans**.
- Bug or failure → **systematic-debugging** before patching.
- All code changes → **test-driven-development** (RED → GREEN); sim work must stay deterministic (`/replay-verify`).

## With Project Aegis studio skills

- Milsim design/production: `.claude/skills/` (`/dev-story`, `/sprint-plan`, GitNexus impact).
- Project plans/specs: `docs/superpowers/` (local docs, not the plugin).
- GitNexus **impact analysis** still required before editing symbols (`Agents.md`).

## Install / update

`.\tools\install-superpowers.ps1` — see `docs/engineering/superpowers-setup.md`.